                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17801206-37-off191 t17801206-37-cd192"></join>, about the hour of nine in the night, and stealing a counterpane, value 14 s. the property of the said 
                     <persName id="t17801206-37-person400">
                        Thomas
                         Darby
                     <interp inst="t17801206-37-person400" type="surname" value="Darby"></interp>
