                  ; a cloth coat, value 15 s. two dimity waistcoats, value 10 s. a pair of velvet breeches, value 10 s. a pair of leather breeches, value 5 s. a linen wrapper, value 1 s. and two pair of silk stockings, the property of 
                     <persName id="t17801206-37-victim401" type="victimName">
                        Banister 
                        Flight
                     <interp inst="t17801206-37-victim401" type="surname" value="Flight"></interp>
